#INSTALLATION

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) INSTALL Miniconda if not installed and create a new environment with python=2.7 
	Miniconda installing: https://docs.conda.io/en/latest/miniconda.html
	Then activate environment before installing. 

2) The rest of installatiion is very simple, in miRPV package you get a install.sh file just type:

	$bash install.sh -p ~/Path/Were/miRPV Package/Present/

This installation might take few minute and install all the dependency require to run the pipeline. If there is some kind of installation error, examine the output above to identify the cause. Or you can install this dependence sepreatly. 

